metadata.name: Kyiv
metadata.description: Kyiv is the heart of Ukraine. A majestic city where history itself tells you its chronicles. From the time when three brothers Kiy, Shchek and Khoryv and their sister Lybid founded the city and named it Kyiv, in honor of their older brother, a lot of water has already flowed from the Dnipro. But it is still a city of glory and pride of the entire Ukrainian nation. If you have not seen this ancient and at the same time eternally young and modern capital, you should definitely do it. And fall in love with it forever!
